graphic:

Power off the machine -> launch VM -> login.

ssh:

Set host ip (127.0.0.1), host port (2222),
guest ip (10.0.2.15 or your IP) and guest port (22)
at VM settings -> network -> advanced -> port forwarding.

Use command ssh username@host_ip -p port to connect on the VM.
# ssh debianpyry@127.0.0.1 -p 2222
